. If it wasn't, I wouldn't have called you on your holiday.\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"p\",[e._v(\"这非常重要，如果不是的话，我就不会在你假期找你了。\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"p\",[e._v(\"And the structure is: If + past simple >> would have + past participle.\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"h3\",{attrs:{id:\"contrasting-ideas-although-despite-and-others\"}},[v(\"a\",{staticClass:\"header-anchor\",attrs:{href:\"#contrasting-ideas-although-despite-and-others\"}},[e._v(\"#\")]),e._v(\" 5️⃣ Contrasting ideas: 'although', 'despite' and others\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"div\",{staticClass:\"custom-block note\"},[v(\"p\",{staticClass:\"custom-block-title\"},[e._v(\"Important\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"p\",[e._v(\"You told me ten times. I still forgot, \"),v(\"strong\",[e._v(\"though\")]),e._v(\".\")])]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"p\",[v(\"strong\",[e._v(\"Although / Even though + sentence\")])]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"p\",[e._v(\"Although we don't agree, I think she's a brilliant speaker.\"),v(\"br\"),e._v(\"\\nEven though we don't agree, I think she's a brilliant speaker.\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"p\",[v(\"strong\",[e._v(\"In spite of / Despite + phrase\")])]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"p\",[e._v(\"In spite of the law, people continue to use mobile phones while driving.\"),v(\"br\"),e._v(\"\\nDespite the law, people continue to use mobile phones while driving.\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"p\",[v(\"strong\",[e._v(\"though 句尾\")])]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"p\",[e._v(\"It's illegal to use mobile phones while driving. People still do it, \"),v(\"strong\",[e._v(\"though\")]),e._v(\".\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"h3\",{attrs:{id:\"different-uses-of-used-to\"}},[v(\"a\",{staticClass:\"header-anchor\",attrs:{href:\"#different-uses-of-used-to\"}},[e._v(\"#\")]),e._v(\" 6️⃣ Different uses of 'used to'\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"div\",{staticClass:\"custom-block note\"},[v(\"p\",{staticClass:\"custom-block-title\"},[e._v(\"MIXTAKE\")]),e._v(\" \"),v(\"ol\",[v(\"li\",[e._v(\"I always hated the cold weather but I \"),v(\"strong\",[e._v(\"got used to\")]),e._v(\" it when I lived in Russia.\")]),e._v(\" \")